  <section class="lp-intro" aria-label="About Global and Teknion">
    <div class="lp-intro__inner">
      <p class="lp-intro__eyebrow bbi-mono">About Global &amp; Teknion</p>
      <h2>Systems furniture that scales from one office to a full floor plan.</h2>
      <div class="lp-intro__body">
        <p>Global Furniture Group and Teknion are part of the same corporate family, offering complementary lines that cover workstations, panel systems, height-adjustable desks, storage, and seating. Global is widely specified for open-plan offices and institutional environments; Teknion offers a broader systems furniture programme with more modular panel and storage options.</p>
        <p>Brant Business Interiors is an authorized dealer for both brands. We provide current spec sheets, finish samples, and CAD blocks for space planning. All products are available under OECM Agreement 2025-470 for eligible Ontario institutional buyers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lp-diff" aria-label="Why Global and Teknion">
    <div class="lp-diff__inner">
      <div class="lp-diff__head">
        <p class="lp-diff__eyebrow bbi-mono">Why Global &amp; Teknion</p>
        <h2>Three reasons institutions specify Global Furniture Group products.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-diff__grid">
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">01</span>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__label">Full-room coordination</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__sentence">Workstations, panels, desks, storage, and seating from a single manufacturer family. Finish coordination across all components — no mix-and-match from disparate catalogues.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">02</span>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__label">Height-adjustable range</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__sentence">Global&rsquo;s height-adjustable desk lines cover sit-stand individual stations and multi-person benching. Teknion adds modular panel-integrated options for larger fit-outs.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">OECM</span>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__label">Pre-qualified for Ontario buyers</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__sentence">All Global and Teknion products are available under OECM Agreement 2025-470. Ontario institutions skip the tender, send us a PO, and we handle the rest.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

