  <section class="lp-faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
    <div class="lp-faq__inner">
      <div class="lp-faq__head">
        <p class="lp-faq__eyebrow bbi-mono">Common questions</p>
        <h2>What buyers ask about Global and Teknion.</h2>
        <p class="lp-faq__cta">Still have a question? <a href="tel:18008359565">Call 1&#8209;800&#8209;835&#8209;9565</a> or <a href="/pages/quote">request a quote</a> and we&rsquo;ll respond in 1 business day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lp-faq__list">

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">01</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">What is the relationship between Global and Teknion?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>Both brands are part of the Global Furniture Group family. Global focuses on chairs, desks, and storage for office and institutional environments at a broad price point. Teknion offers a more comprehensive systems furniture programme &mdash; modular panels, benching, and integrated storage &mdash; often specified for larger open-plan fit-outs. They share finish and laminate palettes, so mixing components between the lines is straightforward.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">02</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">Do you stock Global and Teknion products or are they made to order?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>Most Global and Teknion products are made to order against manufacturer lead times &mdash; typically 4&ndash;8 weeks depending on configuration and finish. Standard-finish, high-volume items (task chairs, standard-depth desks, basic lateral files) can sometimes be sourced from distributor stock for faster delivery. We&rsquo;ll confirm lead time on your quote.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">03</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">Can I get height-adjustable desks in a sit-stand benching configuration?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>Yes &mdash; Global offers individual electric sit-stand desks and multi-person benching with shared legs. Teknion&rsquo;s Expansion line integrates height-adjustable frames into a full panel system if you&rsquo;re doing a complete workstation fit-out. Send us your seating count and footprint and we&rsquo;ll configure the appropriate solution and quote it.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="lp-faq-item">
          <summary>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__num">04</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__q">Are these products available under OECM?</span>
            <span class="lp-faq-item__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="lp-faq-item__body">
            <p>Yes. All Global and Teknion products we carry are available under OECM Agreement 2025-470. Ontario institutional buyers can reference the agreement number on their purchase order and skip the tender process. We&rsquo;ll include the OECM line item on your quote.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

      </div>
